title: Brenda Starr, Reporter 1945 (Old Time Serial)  (OTS)
description:
This is another in the Old Time Serial (OTS) series.  It contains 12 episodes.  It is a series which was shown, one episode per week, in movie theaters in the 1940s and 1950s to keep the kiddies coming back each week to find out about the cliff hanger.  "Did the hero really die this time???"  Of course, he or she never did.
